<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
UNITED STATES -- ECONOMY; WALL STREET; ECONOMIC FORECASTS; ECONOMISTS; 
DEMOGRAPHICS; YARDENI, EDWARD; UNITED STATES -- INDUSTRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031890-0074 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 191212 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 18, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
