<TEXT>
<P>
I absolutely hate that narrow-minded men such as Roger Simon totally 
misunderstand the reasons why Elizabeth Morgan chose to protect her child from 
the child's father even to the lengths that she was willing to spend two years 
in prison. 
</P>
<P>
Please, Mr. Simon, open your mind to the fact that there are fathers who 
sexually abuse their daughters, and there are judges, prosecutors and 
editorialists who simply can't believe this horror is happening. God help the 
children of this country who aren't being protected. 
