<HEADLINE>
<P>
COLLEGE NEWS: AZUSA PACIFIC NURSING SCHOOL OPEN HOUSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Azusa Pacific University, 921 E. Alosta Ave., Azusa, will hold an open house 
for prospective students in its School of Nursing from 9 a.m. to 2 p.m. March 
30. 
</P>
<P>
The event will include a tour of the Nursing Skills Center, a luncheon with 
faculty and students, and information on career opportunities in nursing. 
</P>
</TEXT>
