<HEADLINE>
<P>
COLLEGE NEWS: FUND RAISING BEGINS FOR COLLEGE'S STUDENT PARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
East Los Angeles College in Monterey Park is raising funds for its Student 
Park, a site just east of the college swim stadium. 
</P>
<P>
The site has remained largely undeveloped since it was set aside for a park in 
1981. Plans call for grass and trees to be planted around a modern fast-food 
restaurant, with a fountain in an outdoor eating area and development of an 
outdoor amphitheater. 
</P>
