<TEXT>
<P>
For all those critics of the late Malcolm Forbes' birthday bash of last year: 
He celebrated his life on his last birthday in the grand fashion that he 
wanted. 
</P>
<P>
Who said that he was going to deduct his expenses anyway? He'd only have been 
following the legal guidelines set by our Congress. 
</P>
