CONGRESS (U.S.); NORTHROP CORP; EMPLOYMENT -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; AEROSPACE 
INDUSTRY -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; DEFENSE INDUSTRY -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA 
</P>
