drums at the Vine Street Bar &amp; Grill. DOUGLAS R. BURROWS; Photo, Johnny 
Martinez and his Hollywood Salsa Machine play the Southland six nights a week. 
LARRY GUS / L.A. Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
