<HEADLINE>
<P>
THIS 'SOUTH' WON'T RISE AGAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
One of the biggest disappointments for so many of us was to discover that the 
miniseries "North and South" was not being continued. The potential for an 
immensely romantic and historically significant series created around the Civil 
War era and the nation's recovery would have advertisers beating down the 
network's doors! 
</P>
<P>
Kathleen Fitzgerald, Thousand Oaks 
</P>
